category:            Graphics

synopsis: Tiny library to pretty print sparklines onto the CLI

description: Print sparklines into the CLI. Example usage:
    > import System.Console.Sparkline
    > main = putStrLn . series2spark $ [0, 1, 2, 3, 2, 1]
    output is:
    > _▂▅█▅▂

